									<h5 id="subject_53695">
										<a href="http://forum.17marta.ru/index.php?PHPSESSID=eb8d87982d8139598a665c6c7f23f0b5&amp;topic=8459.msg53695#msg53695" rel="nofollow">Юрий Мухин</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> :</strong> 09/12/12 , 22:58:41 &#187;</div>
